WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:05.200
Our station has two indicator colors: yellow and green. This one is yellow.

00:05.200 --> 00:08.800
When it's yellow I can't process a rental — that means the station is offline.

00:08.800 --> 00:16.300
If I scan the station like this, it won't let me proceed because the device is offline. It's unusable.

00:16.300 --> 00:19.000
What can I do in this situation?

00:19.000 --> 00:25.600
Restart the station: it will detect the SIM again and come back online.

00:25.600 --> 00:30.900
It can also be a Wi-Fi issue. If the station was connected and the password was changed,

00:30.900 --> 00:34.400
we need to edit the Wi-Fi network so it can run again.

00:34.400 --> 00:42.400
With Wi-Fi connected, within a few seconds the color turns from yellow to green — ready to use.
